{"tid":1606204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去到十月一前夕 大家再討論六區定集中都已經冇用","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:30:14.000Z","uid":323753,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bca47f717df873a3f07316347c39c2b06fd92aae","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"去到而家絕大部分冇連登嘅手足都係接收到六區開花嘅資訊 所以即使而家發現六區唔多唔少一定會有人手唔夠嘅情況出現都改唔切 當然集中晒港島都有壞處就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好撚難散</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n我相信冇一個方案會係完全完美 所以既然已經冇得再次更改路線 而家就唯有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家齊齊出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我真係強烈請求多啲港島人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 無論你係勇武定和理非 如果港島真係方便大家散嘅求下大家出黎灣仔 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>因為港島有好撚多重要地帶</strong></span> 已經係肯撚柒定<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>會放最多狗</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你諗下又有支聯辦又政總又狗總咁 一定會想守好自己啲狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但何奈港島人要守住咁多地方真係有一定嘅難度 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以我唔撚該大家係真心撐呢場運動嘅港島人就同我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我何君堯都出黎執葉 你唔係唔出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日齊齊賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4469767439a8538cc6dc8ff0cf76855da88cde59","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d76763f0737167c725091cbf1886b1aa4ab1854","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:41.000Z","msg":"大家聽日都一定要注意安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b500278d067c9bb83564f4ea60039c686b9bed","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7db6db982b91b2a4dd65decd228da60969250be7","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cabf9f99a567b344047e4659277d2e13758dd7","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2a2f462055ed0918450031f6b1509f54a2d7ee","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184e029d799f364a6853a969caeb30d27831ee71","tid":1606204,"uid":323753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci